<br/>
</div>
<figure>
<a href="/news/bombshell-has-gone-gold/"><img src="https://static.3drealms.com/media/article_images/9a9c968d7b824a52ab9c7a235c6b40bb.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Bombshell has gone GOLD!"/></a>
